{"word":"κυβερνάω","slug":"κυβερνάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κυβερνάω</b></el> <el>(κῠβερνάω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>gubernare, to steer</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to act as pilot</i> or <i>helmsman</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to guide, govern</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}